    {
      "span_id": "p048_s0005",
      "text": "4.2.7.1  Description",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.97,
        187.03,
        574.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p048_s0006",
      "text": "The FLOGI/PLOGI ELS shall transfer Service Parameters from the initiating Nx_Port to the FC_Port",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.97,
        540.05,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p048_s0007",
      "text": "associated with the D_ID.  The FLOGI frame provides the means by which an Nx_Port may request",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.97,
        540.03,
        610.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p048_s0008",
      "text": "Login with the Fabric (see 6.2).  The PLOGI frame provides the means by which an Nx_Port may re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.97,
        540.14,
        622.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p048_s0009",
      "text": "quest Login with another Nx_Port prior to other Data frame transfers (see 6.3).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.97,
        442.09,
        634.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p048_s0010",
      "text": "In order to Login with the Fabric and determine the Fabric operating characteristics, an Nx_Port shall",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        647.03,
        540.01,
        658.14
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p048_s0011",
      "text": "specify the D_ID as the well-known F_Port_ID (i.e., FFFFFEh).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        659.03,
        373.68,
        670.14
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
